about.summary: Move OSX dynamic libraries into package

name: delocate
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.7.4" %}

package:
  name: delocate
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: delocate-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/d/delocate/delocate-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 404819b9f4536903c432e9d99c3d5993ba267f86d73cab51d76cc0d6e04dfd55

build:
  number: 1000
  skip: true  # [not osx]
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - wheel

test:
  imports:
    - delocate
  commands:
    - delocate-listdeps -h
    - delocate-wheel -h

about:
  home: https://github.com/matthew-brett/delocate
  license: BSD 2-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Move OSX dynamic libraries into package

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jschueller
